        "# GeoGebra Tasks 07 Planes in Space\n",
        "\n",
        "## 1. Equation of the Plane Passing Through Points A(1, 2, 3), B(3, 4, 5), and C(2, 1, 4):\n",
        "A = (1, 2, 3)\n",
        "B = (3, 4, 5)\n",
        "C = (2, 1, 4)\n",
        "AB = B - A = (3 - 1, 4 - 2, 5 - 3) = (2, 2, 2)\n",
        "AC = C - A = (2 - 1, 1 - 2, 4 - 3) = (1, -1, 1)\n",
        "AB × AC = (2, 2, 2) × (1, -1, 1)\n",
        "(x - 1)(-4) + (y - 2)(4) + (z - 3)(0) = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "## 2. Equation of the Plane Passing Through Point A(1, 2, 3) and Parallel to the Plane 2x + 3y + 4z = 5:\n",
        "A = (1, 2, 3)\n",
        "Plane: 2x + 3y + 4z = 5\n",
        "2(x - 1) + 3(y - 2) + 4(z - 3) = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "## 3. Equation of the Plane Passing Through Point A(1, 2, 3) and Perpendicular to the Normal Vector n→ = [2, 3, 4]:\n",
        "A = (1, 2, 3)\n",
        "2(x - 1) + 3(y - 2) + 4(z - 3) = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "## 4. Find the Line of Intersection of Two Planes: 2x + 3y + 4z = 5 and 3x + 4y + 2z = 6:\n",
        "Plane 1: 2x + 3y + 4z = 5\n",
        "Plane 2: 3x + 4y + 2z = 6\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## 5. Equation of the Plane Passing Through Point A(1, 2, 3) and Parallel to Vectors v1→ = [1, 0, 1] and v2→ = [0, 1, -1]:\n",
        "A = (1, 2, 3)\n",
        "v1→ = [1, 0, 1]\n",
        "v2→ = [0, 1, -1]\n",
        "Equation of the plane:\n",
        "Normal vector • (x - 1, y - 2, z - 3) = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "## 6. Find a Plane Parallel and Perpendicular to the Plane 2x + 3y + 4z = 5:\n",
        "Plane: 2x + 3y + 4z = 5:\n",
        "2x + 3y + 4z = d (for any d ≠ 5)\n",
        "Find an equation of a plane perpendicular to it:\n",
        "Equation of a plane with normal vector (2, 3, 4) and passing through any point.\n",
        "\n",
        "## 7. Find the Distance from Point A(1, 2, 3) to the Plane 2x + 3y + 4z = 5:\n",
        "Plane: 2x + 3y + 4z = 5\n",
        "Point A = (1, 2, 3)\n",
        "Use the distance formula from a point to a plane:\n",
        "Distance = \\(\\frac{|2(1) + 3(2) + 4(3) - 5|}{\\sqrt{2^2 + 3^2 + 4^2}}\\)\n",
        "\n",
        "## 8. Equation of the Plane Passing Through Points A(2, 0, 0), B(0, 3, 0), and C(0, 0, 4):\n",
        "A = (2, 0, 0)\n",
        "B = (0, 3, 0)\n",
        "C = (0, 0, 4)\n",
        "Find vectors AB and AC:\n",
        "AB = B - A = (0 - 2, 3 - 0, 0 - 0) = (-2, 3, 0)\n",
        "AC = C - A = (0 - 2, 0 - 0, 4 - 0) = (-2, 0, 4)\n",
        "Find the cross product of AB and AC to get the normal vector to the plane:\n",
        "Normal vector = AB × AC = (-2, 3, 0) × (-2, 0, 4)\n",
        "Equation of the plane:\n",
        "(x - 2)(12) + (y - 0)(8) + (z - 0)(6) = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "## 9. Calculate the Angle Between the Plane x + y + z = 1 and the Plane x = 0:\n",
        "Plane 1: x + y + z = 1\n",
        "Plane 2: x = 0\n",
        "Find the normal vectors of the planes:\n",
        "Normal to Plane 1 = (1, 1, 1)\n",
        "Normal to Plane 2 = (1, 0, 0)\n",
        "Use the formula for the angle between two planes:\n",
        "cos(θ) = \\(\\frac{|(n1 • n2)|}{\\|n1\\| \\|n2\\|}\\)\n",
        "\n",
        "## 10. Find the Vector Perpendicular to the Plane x + y + z = 1:\n",
        "Plane: x + y + z = 1\n",
        "The normal vector to the plane is:\n",
        "(1, 1, 1)\n"
